### Update Rating Reply
PUT {{baseUrl}}/rating-replies/PUT_REPLY_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reply_text": "Thank you for your valuable feedback! We've shared your comments with our team. We're continuously working to improve our service and hope to welcome you back soon!"
}

### Delete Rating Reply
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/rating-replies/PUT_REPLY_ID_HERE

### Delete All Replies for a Rating
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/rating-replies/rating/PUT_RATING_ID_HERE
